node.text:
With Leah Wyer SVP/GM of @byrdie and Founder/ Partner  of @sblabeauty and me.
I promised I would put up our #instagramlive conversation but as It was a stormy day we lost our connection ( and probably a lot of you 😉) several times so I will post the snippets we were able to salvage . And @sandylinter this one includes a shout out to legendary you. So in case you were #wand-ering …here’s a bit about #sblawands and what the silver neck chin and jawline #wand can do for you! And thank you again @leahwyar for gracing us with your presence you are pure delight! #selfcaresunday 💜💛

node.text: Time to reflect on the report prepared by the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change's latest findings, approved by 195 member states on Friday, which deals with the physical science basis of climate change and outlines how humans are altering the planet in ways that are becoming irreversible and THAT IS A RALLYING CRY for us ALL to act like our house is on fire because it is. The most hardcore  climate change denier can not ignore the historical wildfires and ensuing mud slides snd torrential rains and floods that sweep homes cars and people away the epic super storms off the chart hurricanes and bomb cyclones! Shoreline erosion, mass human migration due to islands sinking into the sea , and inlets with toxic algae blooms coral reefs crumbling as oceans heat up the Gulf Stream’s eminent collapse, drought insect proliferation and disease snd epidemics all predicted and ignored in the first report prepared by the US Dept of Defense because they knew dwindling resources can lead to wars over food and water. My friends we must respond to this with the urgency and attention we owe future generations STARTING NOW! The biggest thing we can do is DEMAND that our representatives react to this report with Wide sweeping changes ..adopting clean green alternative energy and break our dependence on fossil fuels! Let’s keep sharing ways we can make a difference in our daily lives and let’s VOTE IN REPRESENTATIVES that make THIS A PRIORITY! We can do it together because we must!💙🌎💚♻️ #climatechange #climateaction #coderedforhumanity

The Hamptons pride trail is brought to you in partnership with the African Community and Conservation Foundation (ACCF).
This celebration of lions and the people who live alongside them will launch on World Lion Day, 10th August 2021. Life-size lion sculptures, designed and made by some of the planet’s foremost artists, like @donnakaranthewoman  who helped organize #thehamptons artistic community. These lions that will roam the streets to highlight the threats currently faced by ‘the King of Beasts’, and to raise vital funds to support community conservation and livelihoods impacted by Covid-19 across Africa. 
#tuskliontrial #thelionsarecoming

node.text:
A smile is a curve that sets everything straight. — Phyllis Diller
Always laugh when you can. It is cheap medicine. — Lord Byron
As soap is to the body, so laughter is to the soul. — A Jewish Proverb
A good laugh is sunshine in the house. — William Thackeray
Laughter is the closest distance between two people.
Victor Borge
A day without laughter is a day wasted.
Charlie Chaplin
“Laughter is an instant vacation.”
– Milton Berle
“A good time to laugh is any time you can.”
– Linda Ellerbee 
“When humor goes, there goes civilization.”
– Erma Bombeck
“There is nothing in the world so irresistibly contagious as laughter and good humor.”
– Charles Dickens
Come laugh with us! August 22nd One Night Only under the stars ! Live at the elegant outdoor theatre

the hit play  @celeb_autobio with a galaxy of sparkling superstars  @therealsusanlucci the one and only #mathewbroderick

see you there!💙
